Package: evictionAddresses
Title: Eviction Address Collection and Validation for OSCN Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Brancen", "Gregory", ,
      "brancengregory@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for collecting, validating, and geocoding eviction 
    addresses from the Oklahoma State Courts Network (OSCN). Includes a data-entry 
    dashboard and API for processing eviction case data, address verification through 
    Postgrid, and utility functions for pay period calculations and data processing.
